131
00:13:23,895 --> 00:13:27,148
U prolazu?
- Da.

132
00:13:27,232 --> 00:13:29,192
Tako si beo.

133
00:13:31,528 --> 00:13:34,113
Jesi li ikad videla nekog
ovako belog, Mardž?

134
00:13:34,197 --> 00:13:36,157
Sivog, ustvari.

135
00:13:36,241 --> 00:13:38,743
To je samo potkošulja.

136
00:13:38,827 --> 00:13:42,413
Reci opet?
- Znaš...potkošulja.

137
00:13:44,833 --> 00:13:46,668
Smešno.

138
00:13:46,751 --> 00:13:49,671
Mardži to voli,
jer je i ona tako bela.

139
00:13:49,712 --> 00:13:51,422
Da, volim,
a ti nisi tako smešan.

140
00:13:51,464 --> 00:13:53,842
Mogli bi smo da ručamo zajedno,
pre nego što odeš.

141
00:13:53,883 --> 00:13:56,678
Važi, Diki?
- Naravno, kad hoćeš.

142
00:13:56,719 --> 00:13:59,180
