210
00:17:31,730 --> 00:17:34,233
ćao, Fausto.

211
00:17:38,237 --> 00:17:40,740
Ovo je Tom.
- ćao, Tom.

212
00:17:42,992 --> 00:17:45,537
Nikad se neću vratiti.
- Ne, mislim...

213
00:17:45,578 --> 00:17:47,580
Tvoja majka...njena bolest.
Mislim da je...

214
00:17:47,622 --> 00:17:50,708
To nema veze sa mojom majkom.

215
