382
00:31:14,110 --> 00:31:17,071
Ne.

383
00:31:17,113 --> 00:31:19,240
Ni braće, ni sestre.

384
00:31:21,493 --> 00:31:23,953
Ni ja.

385
00:31:24,037 --> 00:31:26,206
Nema ni Mardž.

386
00:31:27,832 --> 00:31:30,585
Svi smo jedinci.

387
00:31:36,591 --> 00:31:38,718
Šta to znači?

388
00:31:40,929 --> 00:31:43,389
Znači da nikad nismo
delili kupatilo.

389
00:31:47,352 --> 00:31:50,271
Hladno mi je.
Mogu li unutra?

390
00:31:55,528 --> 00:31:58,197
Ne.

391
